{"type":null,"faqId":31610,"title":"How do I track single activity using my TalkBand B2?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Wake up the TalkBand B2 screen and swipe until you reach the activity screen     </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98350\" style=\"width:0.3263889in;height:0.6472222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> .</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Touch the start icon for 3 seconds and your TalkBand B2 will begin recording activity data.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98351\" style=\"width:0.26875in;height:0.22638889in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> : Pause</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98352\" style=\"width:0.27847221in;height:0.21736111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> : Resume</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=98353\" style=\"width:0.2777778in;height:0.2in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> : View the activity duration, data, and calories burned</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":328,"faqType":"Fitness and Health Monitoring","useful":4,"unUseful":2,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"6110","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Sports-Health-Monitoring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435059512000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":104,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileN